---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Johannesburg Bible Study Church"
  description="Privacy policy for Johannesburg Bible Study Church website. Information about how we collect, use, and protect your data."
>
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-max max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="heading-1 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: June 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-8">
        <p>
          Johannesburg Bible Study Church ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard information when you visit our website.
        </p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Contact information</strong> — name and phone number when you contact us by phone</li>
          <li><strong>Usage data</strong> — pages visited, browser type, and approximate location via standard analytics</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies</strong> — small files stored on your device to improve website functionality</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your information to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond to your enquiries via phone</li>
          <li>Improve our website and user experience</li>
          <li>Provide information about Bible study sessions and community classes</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          Our website may use essential cookies for basic functionality. Analytics cookies (if used) help us understand how visitors use the site. You can disable cookies in your browser settings if you prefer.
        </p>

        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          Our website may include embedded content (such as Google Maps or Google Meet links) or analytics tools. These services have their own privacy policies governing their use of your data.
        </p>

        <h2>Google AdSense</h2>
        <p>
          We may display Google AdSense advertisements on this website. Google uses cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits. You can opt out of personalised advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          Contact enquiries are handled directly by phone and are not stored digitally beyond what is necessary to respond to your enquiry.
        </p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          You have the right to request access to, correction of, or deletion of any personal data we may hold about you. To make such a request, please contact us by phone.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your data, please contact us by phone at <a href="tel:+27774871295" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">+27 77 487 1295</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
